==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Brant
<hw>Brant</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>brant</ets>; akin to Dan.
<ets>brat</ets>, Icel. <ets>brattr</ets>, steep.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Steep; high.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Grapes grow on the <qex>brant</qex> rocks so wonderfully that ye
will marvel how any man dare climb up to them.</q>
<rj><qau>Ascham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Smooth; unwrinkled.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your bonnie brow was <qex>brent</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Burns.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Brent</ent>⟦br⟧
